@section('content')

    <section id="About" class="overflow-x-hidden">
        <div class="container p-[2rem]" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-4">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-[#031D26] text-[2rem]">About <span class="text-[#B11515]"> Us </span></h1>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-[2rem] text-sm w-[85%] mx-auto text-[#4e4e4e]">
                <p class="py-1">Welcome to the Mukhtaran Rafiq Welfare Hospital! We are an incredible initiative of the Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation, committed to offering free medical treatment to underprivileged individuals in Lahore, Pakistan. Our journey began in May 2004, with a small dispensary aimed at addressing the lack of accessible healthcare in our local community. However, in response to the growing number of patients seeking our help, we recognized the need to expand our services. Today, we have evolved into a remarkable 30-bed hospital, striving to enhance healthcare accessibility for the poor and needy, particularly those from disadvantaged backgrounds. <br></p>
                <p class="py-1"> In 2012, the Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation acquired a plot in Harbanspura, Lahore, which was generously bestowed to the hospital. This enabled us to upgrade our facilities and register with the Social Welfare Department, securing A tax exemption certificate. Building on this progress, we further expanded our hospital in 2014 to accommodate 20 additional beds, as well as an operation theatre and labor room. This expansion has allowed us to offer a wider range of medical services to our patients. <br></p></p>
                <p class="py-1">In recognition of our efforts, the Social Welfare Department bestowed upon us the prestigious Best Achievement Award in 2017, affirming our dedication to providing exceptional healthcare. At present, we serve approximately 350 - 400 patients daily, with a significant portion of them receiving our services free of charge. Annually, we treat around 150,000 patients with 15,000 of them benefiting from complimentary checkups, medicine and vital treatments. <br></p>
                <p class="py-1">Our hospital is a four-story building comprising state of the art emergency room, general wards, state-of-the-art operation theaters, patient rooms, and numerous medical departments. These departments include 24/7 Opd/Emergency, Orthopedic Surgery, General Surgery, Gynecology, Infertility, Dentistry, Diabetes, Family Medicine, Diagnostic Laboratory, Radiology, X-ray, Physiotherapy, Nutrition, E.N.T, Pulmonology, Dermatology, Psychiatry, Urology, And Gerontology. </p>
                <p class="py-1">We take great pride in offering free dialysis services to all our patients, further demonstrating our commitment to supporting those in need. In addition to our hospital services we regularly organize free medical camps. These camps provide top-notch medical checkups and complimentary me.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="Who" class="overflow-x-hidden">
        <div class="container p-[2rem]" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-4">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-[#031D26] text-[2rem]">Who <span class="text-[#B11515]"> We Are </span></h1>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-[2rem] text-sm w-[85%] mx-auto text-[#4e4e4e]">
                <p class="py-1">Mukhtaran Rafiq Welfare Hospital operates under the guidance of the Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation (MRF) which is an independent, non-political, non-profit and non-governmental organization focused on social welfare. We are proud to be registered with the Punjab Healthcare Commission (PHC), Social Welfare Department (SWD), Punjab Charity Commission (PCC) & other bodies related to healthcare. </p>
                <p class="py-1"> Our mission is to provide free healthcare services to underprivileged individuals in Lahore, Pakistan. We started as a small dispensary in May 2004 and quickly grew into a 30-bed hospital. We aim to enhance healthcare accessibility for the poor and needy, regardless of their financial circumstances. Our dedicated team offers a wide range of medical services, including consultations, diagnostics, surgeries and post-operative care. Through partnerships and generous support, we strive to sustain and expand our services to bring positive change in the lives of those in need. Join us in supporting our mission to provide free healthcare services to the underprivileged.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="overflow-x-hidden" id="President">
        <div class="container p-[2rem] w-[95%]" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-4">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-[#031D26] text-[2rem]">President's <span class="text-[#B11515]">Message</span>
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-[2rem] grid grid-cols-1 gap-[2rem]">
                <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
                    <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/Abdul%20Majeed.jpg')}}" class="rounded-md w-100vw h-[30rem] object-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-[100%] justify-center">

                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm text-[#4e4e4e]">
                        <b>Accessible Healthcare</b>
                        <b> Compassionate Service</b>
                        <p class="py-1">The Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation, driven by the belief that serving humanity is a noble practice cherished by all religions and societies, is dedicated to making a positive impact in society. To seek Allah's acceptance and fulfill the desires of every individual to elevate their worldly and eternal lives, the foundation tirelessly serves humanity. </p>
                        <p class="py-1">Since our establishment in 2004 as a small dispensary & after the continuous efforts of two decades, Mukhtaran Rafiq Welfare Hospital has grown into a state-of-the-art hospital with four stories, offering a range of services, including both out-patient and in-patient care, specialist clinics, operation theater, ICU, labor rooms and a diagnostic laboratory. We also provide 24/7 emergency services, ensuring that immediate medical attention is available whenever needed.</p>
                        <p class="py-1">  At Mukhtaran Rafiq Welfare Hospital, we strongly believe in making healthcare services accessible and affordable to all, regardless of their financial status. By offering free medical services, we aim to alleviate the burden of expensive healthcare costs faced by major communities in our society.</p>
                        <p class="py-1">As President of the Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation, I am dedicated to providing advanced and quality healthcare services to all individuals, regardless of their circumstances. Our vision is to ensure everyone has access to the medical care they need. With our team and community support, we will make a difference in the lives of those in need.
                        <p class="py-1">  May Allah almighty guide us all in our sincere endeavors “Ameen”.

                        </p>
                        <b>Abdul Majeed</b>
                        <b>President</b>
                        <b>Mukhtaran Rafiq Foundation</b>


